Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:47.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い事　揺れる音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:50.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとひそめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:58.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頬のそばで舞う雪達…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:05.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たくさんの後悔　過去を結ぶ笑顔たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風のささやき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:11.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れて溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:19.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冬空の淋しさを重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:27.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさの瞳越えて　今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:35.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいメロディ　指差した一番星光る空に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:43.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描き集めた未来　かじかんだ指の隙間通る星座たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:51.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah　この場所から見た景色　叶えたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:57.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約束ね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:47.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的愿望  摇曳的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:50.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:58.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让飞雪滑过脸颊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:05.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}挥之不去的后悔  紧系过去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北风的细语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:11.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一触即散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:19.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夹杂着寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:27.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越过了眼中的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:35.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在想给你的旋律  遥指着初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:43.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼凑出的未来  手指间露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:51.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要实现在此看见的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:57.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}约定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揺れる水面　その深くに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青い宇宙映ってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来…そしてまた散っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}季節覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちは運命紡ぎながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その糸がどこまで続いてくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(ただそこに)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}inspiration　喜びとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉を分かち合うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああいつか終わりの日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう感じさせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}initialize　その扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}開ける時が来るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綺麗な時を閉じ込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}湖に沈めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど私平気だよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星の便りに綴る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在涟漪的水面深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照映着蔚蓝的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来又将飘零而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}唯此季节长存心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我们编织命运之丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}却从来都不曾知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这丝线将通向何处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(仅仅伫立于此)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}每当我与他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}灵感乍现时的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就已经隐约察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终会有结束的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}重置人生的那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终有渐渐打开之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}美好时光关入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再慢慢地沉入湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不过我会在星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}写下一句「我没事」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经说过好多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这忽然是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没睡醒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天收拾搬家的行李弄到很晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:00:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到刚才我都跟诺艾尔一起在天文台的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也认识的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还帮我救了诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  能看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:08.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(418,270)}「没有飞碟的小镇」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从东京过来的长途旅行累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是暑假？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…已经下过雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你梦里的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到家之后  稍微休息一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你还记得家在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来观光的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  在哪里见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不可能会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…刚才大家还一起在天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文台？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是乃乃香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候开始就没见过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香什么都没说就从小镇上消失了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很担心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…七年前的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了这么久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到刚才为止明明还是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但诺艾尔消失了  飞碟也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不是很明白那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能再会真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外国人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五个人一起聚集在天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常在那里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后大家一起做的那件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤飞碟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手牵着手围成圈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许下愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟什么的  怎么可能会来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是相信着的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上不是什么都没有发生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有这么想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个时候  飞碟真的出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你为什么会知道我的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然记得  小时候还一起在天文台玩耍来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里  装了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  做得很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  不介意的话  之后一起去湖边发射试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起发射过的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候  聚集在天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起呼唤飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  做过这样的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟真的出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟来到小镇了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香你居然会说这种笑话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟  诺艾尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一点都记不得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  回忆起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重要的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去问一下凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我们交换联系方式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  柚季  我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  请问住这里的户川汐音…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  这里没有这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没人知道飞碟的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}优子  你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是  骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还记得诺艾尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李全都搬进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我们一起大扫除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说  从一开始就没来过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋两个  半熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}下一条新闻…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开学典礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在同一个班就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫古宫乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宫同学因为父亲工作的原因  从东京转学过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要和她好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古宫同学  你的座位在第二列的最后一行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在同一个班  真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  难得乃乃香回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去哪里玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我有事想告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于天文台的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  要叫上凑太吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想知道乃乃香你到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后  汐音她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道她在哪个班级吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学的时候  她搬去很远的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音一直想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}抱歉  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有联系方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}嗯  是的  现在我们去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和汐音  5个人一起呼唤飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在可能记不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在我所知道的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个在湖上空的飞碟和名叫诺艾尔的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我们都忘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟小镇  大家也都是曾有目共睹的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香是在天文台认识的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在也还是最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很想相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的会有飞碟来实现大家的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是件非常美好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也很想相信乃乃香说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么事都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是关于诺艾尔的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和诺艾尔一起度过的时光里发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话语  表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只想起来一点点也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  诺艾尔会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不想用这种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这会不会只是你的臆想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为记得那个叫诺艾尔的人的…只有乃乃香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你梦里的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔为了实现大家的愿望…明明那么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  凑太也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都曾见过那样的诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  再说下去也没有意义了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  凑太  能不能不用这种语气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太说的对  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一个人呆一会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}诺艾尔是真实存在的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有我记得诺艾尔了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连我也忘记了诺艾尔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或许真的就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下所有…我关于诺艾尔的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明能飞得更高的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底少了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会如此焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  一直守护着这座小镇的你应该是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们或许失去了  最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔  我想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了  快出现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次在我面前欢笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…会发生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的全部都是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔真的不存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  七年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗  小时候曾在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所记得的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所记得的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在流星雨之夜见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子眼中的泪光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔最喜欢的可不是这种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
